{
 "name": "RPlog_Operation_Shado_Kolpo_-_Fifth_Wave",
 "title": "Operation Shado Kolpo: Fifth Wave",
 "summary": "Aboard the Imperial Star Destroyer Broadsword, Captain Caiton and Count Diaglo grimly vow to reclaim and cleanse Caiton's family homeworld as the ISB-informed Imperial fleet sets its blockade to crush the New Republic's attempt to run freighters into besieged Coruscant. The Republic escort force, with Lt. Krieg Inrokana's War Shrikes and pilots like Aramis, Alex, Keline, and Allerdyce, drives toward the gap, but the trap closes around them. In the ensuing carnage the leading carrack Admiral Rishar is crippled and its commander sounds a doomed retreat, the freighters mangled and destroyed. With the operation broken, the agent Jal'Dana reports the Republic's failure to her Lord, and the Imperial battle group tightens its noose around Coruscant.",
